Text: MUM TO AHD BY TRAIN IN 5 HRS 30 MINS
AN HOUR LESS THAN EXISTING DAY TRAINS
Vande Bharat Express, which will run between Mumbai Central and
Gandhinagar from Sept 30 onwards, will take only 6 hours and 20 minutes
to go between the two state capitals, and only 5 hours and 35 minutes
from Mumbai to Ahmedabad. Manthan K Mehta reports
Vande Bharat Express I Train no: 20901/2
